{"tid":645132,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"用iphone嘅你會唔會用siri......","createTime":"2018-04-27T23:10:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-29T19:09:31.000Z","uid":166264,"like":12,"dislike":125,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"9d5dfa207d20116038f519e8cb01dc7a41aaaf7e","tid":645132,"uid":166264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T23:10:53.000Z","msg":"話說有日無聊走去玩siri <br />\n跟住試下用取消鬧鐘<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/28/070237_754bc8a5a2d33cf09ff86ad87a142743.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F28%2F070237_754bc8a5a2d33cf09ff86ad87a142743.png&h=2946ac26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n平時iphone個鬧鐘咪好鬼煩<br />\n鎖左moon熄佢咪會去賴床模式<br />\n跟住9分鐘就重響 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無間地獄<br />\n跟住用siri熄鬧鐘係唔會重響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可以一覺瞓到一點<br />\n呢三日我已經遲左兩日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要開埋喂，siri 跟本只係講一句就瞓到夠鐘食下午茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf0729b971dd19f40c52979463dc9f1319fd63c9","tid":645132,"uid":35815,"like":68,"dislike":1,"score":67,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T23:50:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2ca1bb6f4473accccc8cd53bb786228b48d5e51d","tid":645132,"uid":9115,"like":44,"dislike":5,"score":39,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T00:07:03.000Z","msg":"我成日用嚟set鬧鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n開個setting出嚟有排碌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n用siri一句搞惦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f2baf16dc6d5489b610163628749d67b43dac7b","tid":645132,"uid":8048,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T00:08:01.000Z","msg":"